      • pull

        PubSubRpc.PullFuture pull(com.google.pubsub.v1.PullRequest request)
        Sends a request to pull messages from a subscription. This method returns a PubSubRpc.PullFuture object to consume the result. Future.get() returns a response object containing the pulled messages. PullFuture#addCallback(PullCallback) can be used to register a callback for the request's completion.
        Parameters:
        request - the request object containing all of the parameters for the API call
